eners stage full product ready industry business products location north huntingdon pa usa currency usd founded april  employees  website pittmosscom company summary pittmoss development co llc makes and markets pittmoss® a sustainable alternative to sphagnum peat moss which is the highest most lucrative grade of peat commercial greenhouse and nursery operations consume approximately  of the  million ton annual us market in their soil blends and are the least cyclical most repetitive peat moss consumers growing as many as five annual crops globally the market for peat is  million tons team mont andrew handley presidentceo mont handley the inventor of pittmoss® and founder of pittmoss development co holds a ba in history from purdue university his career began managing the livegoods department of five frank’s nursery locations in suburban chicago during that time he began to develop the product that eventually earned us patent   which is the foundational basis for pittmoss® handley moved to pittsburgh in  to work for visitpittsburgh matt collins knapp director of operations matt knapp a native of suburban pittsburgh has career experience at recycling facilities and is our product mix master matts recycling industry experience includes weshred a document shredding company and monongalia county solid waste authority in morgantown west virginia he is the primary operator of manufacturing equipment and began working for pittmoss development co llc during the custom plant development phase in march  vince joseph angellotto director of sales vince or vj angellotto earned a ba in marketing from indiana university of pennsylvania and has served as the director of sales as of september   his national sales and marketing experience in the freight industry has been very beneficial to pittmoss development co llc understanding of shipping costs and savings opportunities vj engages customers directly and manages the company saleforcecom customer relationship database mont handley 